Name: Initiative
Description: High level Issue type for planning

Name: Epic
Description: A big user story that needs to be broken down. Created by Jira Software - do not edit or delete.

Name: Story
Description: Functionality or a feature expressed as a user goal.

Name: Task
Description: A small, distinct piece of work.

Name: Sub-task
Description: A small piece of work that's part of a larger task.

Name: Spike
Description: A story that cannot be estimated until a development team runs a time-boxed investigation. The output of a spike is an estimate for the original story.
